99.text: Now, it's music time～♪ \nWhich song is Trainer-san's favorite～?

149.text: Hm, hmm, hm～ hnn～…\nOh my, am I too slow～?

150.text: Here we go～! When Falcon runs～? One, two… "We run after her!" Ehe♪ Thanks everyone☆

151.text: Wah～ They're all great songs! Tell me your favorite, trainer♪

152.text: Eyy don't run off, listen! The waves'll leave a Golshi shaped impression on your eardrums…☆

153.text: This tone reverberates in my heart. What sort of tracks do you prefer, Trainer?

154.text: Music keeps me running! \nWhat songs do you like to run to?

155.text: Oho, what a great selection of tracks \nI see you have great taste～!

156.text: Put on something energetic to dance to!

157.text: Huh, I like this track! The sounds are filling my head with amazing magics!

158.text: Music? …I don't hate it. Lets me shut out the noise.

159.text: Hearing these songs reminds \nme of my rivals!

174.text: Songs that bring luck change \nwith time! Isn't that interesting?

175.text: Now that's a spiffy tune…! \nI can't wait ta be a "city girl" \nbefitting of them vibes～…!

176.text: What a very, very nice song～! \nWhat dance would fit it?

183.text: DJ Heli in da house! \nPut your hands up, it's party time!

184.text: Gotta go fast, WEEEII! \nI wanna have a blast singing \nmy lungs out with Milady again～♪

187.text: This sound is special to me. Like a gust \nof wind rushing through my heart, leaving \nits lingering scent... I cherish it.
